GB DEAGLE (FINAL)
=================

author...........Electronaut     
date completed...01.04.2006
version..........1.0.0
game type........Counter-Strike: Source
map type.........Generated Boxes (gb_*), Fight Yard (fy_*), Deagle Map

Information:
------------

This is a deagle map I created that provides some randomness to the paths from
one side of the level to the other. I devised several different pathways to be
opened up in the map, which are picked at random after every spawn.  This means
that the way a player went one round will most likely not be available to him/her
next round. This makes the game a bit more adaptive.

Additional Notes:
-----------------
  * There are no buy zones in this map.  Deagles, kevlar armor
    and helmets are given to each player at the beginning of 
    the map.
  * There is one custom texture used in this map, and it was
    added to the BSP file using bspzip, meaning there are no
    textures needing to be unzipped, making it for easier
    installation. 1/2 of the texture is on the billboard on
    one of the walls, and the other is in an easter egg room
    located below the center of the warehouse.
